{"tid":860052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"25億淺水灣豪宅面臨充公","createTime":"2018-10-13T04:49:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T05:28:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"55ccb3bf2a3d0f395b09f9e89939f55975dead1c","tid":860052,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T04:49:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181013/20521408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181013%2F20521408&d=pEZI3lDOW5PHS5Aq%2FwRrlDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=6592f248\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181013%2F20521408&h=cff171cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181013/20521408</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月13日 <br />\n<br />\n25億淺水灣豪宅面臨充公<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181013/large/a1603a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181013%2Flarge%2Fa1603a.gif&h=be9b3cfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】流亡美國的郭文貴，盛傳擁有香港居民身份和特區護照，並在淺水灣南灣道擁有巿值近25億港元的獨立屋豪宅（圖），但大宅因為有至少十處違規僭建，並未經批准填海、霸佔政府保護海岸區、肆意斬樹，去年已被地政總署釘契，整幅土地面臨被充公。<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴與關連人士於2011年以英屬處女島公司「耀領有限公司」的名義，在港以8.8億港元買入南灣道20及22號獨立屋。郭買入大宅後大肆裝修，耗費近6億港元。<br />\n<br />\n屋宇署在2015年已向20及22號屋業主發出清拆令，指裝修工程涉十項違規。地政總署去年5月指，該大宅進佔保護海岸區並霸佔了947方呎政府土地作違例建築，已作出釘契，稍後會視乎業主是否清拆，考慮進一步執管行動。<br />\n<br />\n另外，香港法庭文件顯示，警方懷疑郭文貴及其兒子郭強、女兒郭美等人涉嫌洗錢達329億港元，已凍結了郭美的企業戶口。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兒女涉在港洗錢<br />\n<br />\n郭美持有的安東發展有限公司，今年8月入稟香港高院申請司法覆核，指公司戶口被凍結太久，造成財政困難，認為警方做法違反《基本法》中關於私有財產權的條款。法庭文件顯示，郭美是安東及香港國際基金投資公司的持有人。<br />\n<br />\n申請人稱，去年7月獲星展銀行知會，警方以「不同意處理制度」，要求凍結安東五個戶口，其中3個賬戶分別有9,300萬美元（7.25億港元）、港幣8,300萬元及人民幣300萬元（340萬港元），另外兩個賬戶資產不明。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n村童變大鱷　揭王岐山醜聞出位<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n孟宏偉妻被指小三　掛名任港企高層<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n村童變大鱷　揭王岐山醜聞出位<br />\n<br />\n政泉控股被判強迫交易罪成中共狙擊郭文貴　重罰681億元"},{"pid":"d837cc95b02d396682075e254baeafe206f0b465","tid":860052,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T04:59:45.000Z","msg":"原來係郭文貴"},{"pid":"abc4d76bf24170159ed78a9111568df41345fb14","tid":860052,"uid":18955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:05:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bf019f3c7b8d0b31cd15ce129a5e3874c1f8f10","tid":860052,"uid":17859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:08:14.000Z","msg":"已經同支那完全接軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2542d47d421faa11e7c82ef41033d19c952d43f","tid":860052,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:09:05.000Z","msg":"試吓係香港富豪<br />\n政府幫佢起埋路"},{"pid":"779efbbf082f40b4bfa8702387f423bb607acca7","tid":860052,"uid":81671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:09:23.000Z","msg":"有錢到自己填海？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4ba658c40ffa436a4e6bad0277489f12c8cd6c","tid":860052,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:09:38.000Z","msg":"上頭命令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3cc42c58012dd6bbb541b23bfcd4bdc1825827f","tid":860052,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:11:17.000Z","msg":"洗錢過大海得啦，賭一賭全部變乾淨錢"},{"pid":"049aa2d8a9893b085e54737d4c3c9ef05a64e9de","tid":860052,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci